# need BLE variables for

Wifi SSID
Wifi password
server IP address (or name)

==> initiate Wifi connection


throttle name (used for WIFI hostname, BLE device name, WiThrottle name)


loco address to select
==> initiate locomotive selection
==> release locomotive

swap direction toggle
function mapping (e.g., BRAKE => F9)


speed
direction
function state
function names  (these can change on the fly, with an address selection)

fast time (read from withrottle server, update to app via BLE)
real time (read from phone, update RTC/logging on the throttle)
